{"tid":2170101,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"BLM運動發起人Patrisse Cullors：拜登支持BLM，只是Lip Service（得把口）","createTime":"2020-08-23T04:42:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-27T11:37:11.000Z","uid":48040,"like":46,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"d44ff0c7609e246947f9cb70c710526ddfc77d53","tid":2170101,"uid":48040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T04:42:25.000Z","msg":"Joe Biden在民主黨大會召開的第一天晚上請了George Floyd的兄弟和Eric Garner的母親。在第三天晚上，希拉里&middot;克林頓和巴拉克&middot;奧巴馬說了「黑人生命很重要」。<br />\n<br />\n表態支持黑人平權，是民主黨這次大會的重大轉變，BLM的推動者並非沒有註意到這一點。<span class=\"orange\">但其BLM運動領導人認為這些表態，口惠而實不至（lip service)，</span>而沒有真正致力於政策改變：他們希望拜登承諾削減警察預算撥款並打擊執法不當行為。<br />\n<br />\n「不幸的是，沒有看到民主黨完全支持該運動，」Patriss Cullors說，他在Trayvon Martin被殺後於2013年幫助創立了BLM運動。<br />\n<br />\n拜登的競選活動與許多BLM推動者之間持續出現分歧，雖然他們在反對特朗普連任上立場一致。<span class=\"orange\">這顯示了民主黨人試圖走的謹慎路線：儘管BLM運動已成為主流，但大多數美國人告訴民意測驗人員，他們不支持削減警察的預算撥款。</span><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"orange\">拜登試圖做「騎牆派」，既支持BLM運動，而又不疏遠搖擺選民</span>。他在提名講話中談到&ldquo;種族主義污點&rdquo;，但未提供政策上的解決辦法。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/EagleNews_HK/status/1297190479415504898?s=20\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FEagleNews_HK%2Fstatus%2F1297190479415504898%3Fs%3D20&d=MZ%2BcikgbnzcLbT%2Fpq7%2BWTGyprV%2B6HEKZLwhfW4p%2FhGU%3D&h=5702487e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FEagleNews_HK%2Fstatus%2F1297190479415504898%3Fs%3D20&h=f95b2f34\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/EagleNews_HK/status/1297190479415504898?s=20</a>"},{"pid":"dfb1cff5e735ab8e32fd5444453aa309d4d562a7","tid":2170101,"uid":370061,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T04:44:07.000Z","msg":"狗咬狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89edfe0133995b228d7259936f46d975281fcd4a","tid":2170101,"uid":310700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T04:44:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\"